Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.89,0:00:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have one sip
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.35,0:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,of some good old
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.07,0:00:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,that'll
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.53,0:00:27.32,Default,,0,0,0,,last me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.32,0:00:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to check with headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,to see how things are going periodically
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,alright we were going to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,we're finishing up with the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.49,0:00:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,last of the
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.22,0:00:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,valuable qualities of a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.72,0:00:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.89,0:01:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,the qualities of a spiritual seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.11,0:01:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,then takes advantage
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,of the consciousness of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher aside from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.09,0:01:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,what's said aside from
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.09,0:01:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what you think is going on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.68,0:01:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,none of that's happening
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.62,0:01:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the field
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the field of the teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.40,0:01:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because the power of the field
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.42,0:01:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,of the teacher has come on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.00,0:01:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,has come down through the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.90,0:01:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so whatever is speaking to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.53,0:01:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to you today
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,is the accumulation of the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.09,0:01:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,influence of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.01,0:01:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,speakers of teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,going back to the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.09,0:01:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,so the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.29,0:01:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the energy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.78,0:01:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.50,0:02:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is there now available
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.17,0:02:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,resist
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.87,0:02:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,so every great teacher who ever lived
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,leaves the
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.18,0:02:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,power of the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the Buddha
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.33,0:02:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of that field
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,within the collective consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.59,0:02:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's why mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.28,0:02:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,progresses
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.46,0:02:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise if you had to start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.24,0:02:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,from zero every time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.93,0:02:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,every generation had to start
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.41,0:02:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,from scratch
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind would not be
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,where it is today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of every great teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,who has ever lived remains
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.53,0:02:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and is still available
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to focus on a particular
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.90,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,or a teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,or their teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.99,0:02:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,by meditating or visiting them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,or going to lectures or whatever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of that teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,you know is now available
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:58.99,Default,,0,0,0,,to the seeker
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.99,0:03:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,alright so down through the centuries
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.59,0:03:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the great beings
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.53,0:03:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is now here present
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.21,0:03:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,resist
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.06,0:03:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is now here available
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.68,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,to every student
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.37,0:03:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and is the karmic or their
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,karmic right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.97,0:03:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,their karmic right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,it's your right
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.47,0:03:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,by virtue of your declaration
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.15,0:03:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to benefit from the consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.43,0:03:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,of all the great teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,who have ever lived
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,that's pretty good huh
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.47,0:03:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,what is today May 31st
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.56,0:03:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,May 21st
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,so the world's not coming to an end at all
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,oh well
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought for excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.71,0:03:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,it's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,it's hard to beat you know
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.68,0:03:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,haven't they
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.18,0:03:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,for excitement
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.74,0:04:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't beat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,beat the end of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,history
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.93,0:04:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the end of mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,okay
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.41,0:04:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,it is the will of every truly enlightened teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,that every student succeed
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.09,0:04:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and not just limited
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to a particular group
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,you will hear that weakness
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.60,0:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and defect
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in various world religions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and spiritual groups
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.22,0:04:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,that they are select
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.42,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's only their enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,they're worried about, and you're an infidel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,So beware of those who see everybody but themselves as infidels.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.31,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think that's a good warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,See, that is indeed a good warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha, those who think heaven and salvation is only for them
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,are in error.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.55,0:05:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.62,0:05:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They are in error, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.25,0:05:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, salvation and enlightenment is for all of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, because it is the will of God, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It is the will of every truly enlightened sage
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that every seeker succeed,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,not just members of your congregation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.60,0:05:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as the individual seeker benefits mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,thus also.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the enlightenment of the teacher benefit the seeker?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:47.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The teacher benefits from the student,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.75,0:05:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,and the student benefits from the teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.35,0:06:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The spiritual power of every great teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,who has ever lived is currently available
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,through the consciousness of one's current teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.68,0:06:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.02,0:06:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the consciousness that speaks to this audience now
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.50,0:06:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is empowered by all the great teachers
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.89,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,that have ever lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:35.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.48,0:06:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, what a responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.18,0:06:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I was going to take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So out of thanks,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,you hold your own spiritual advancement
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and intention and enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,for the benefit of everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Not just for the benefit of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What you're doing for yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.48,0:07:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,you do for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.75,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So be conscious of that fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.76,0:07:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that your prayers,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.25,0:07:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,your enlightenment,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.58,0:07:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the progression of your level of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.75,0:07:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,benefits all of mankind,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and it is your gift to mankind
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that you share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.50,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, your being here today
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,is a gift to all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The presence of all now present
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is a gift to all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.30,0:07:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.77,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind thanks you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.23,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.25,0:07:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, good old Doc Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He keeps going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.85,0:07:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to take care of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.85,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My job is to see he doesn't forget his cane
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.26,0:08:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and fall over the edge of the front of your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.26,0:08:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.08,0:08:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.12,0:08:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.07,0:08:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a great man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.07,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no requirements or obligations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sign up for anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.63,0:08:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to agree to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.63,0:08:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go into a contractual agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.02,0:08:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God is both manifest as the totality and allness of creation
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and same with God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.48,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.48,0:08:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Unmanifest as the Godhead, the source of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God is infinite beyond time or depiction of space or locality
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.59,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,without beginning or ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I thought God lived down the street there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.84,0:09:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't just live in church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, probably yourself like all of us all his family
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.78,0:09:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us as kids thought that God lived in the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.13,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Did everybody think God lived in the church?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that God lived in the church, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.00,0:09:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I was very careful when I got into the block that had a church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.65,0:09:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd walk around, I'd be careful I didn't have any sinful thoughts or anything like that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.96,0:09:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because this is where God lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.94,0:09:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,God lived in the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.37,0:09:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's sort of cute in a way, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The church was God's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.23,0:10:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I guess that's the way it's phrased so that children understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're not children anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know that God is all the time everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.99,0:10:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Used to be fun walking down, getting closer and closer to the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now God's everywhere. He's in the grocery store.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.77,0:10:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,God is in the supermarket. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God. God's in the supermarket.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,RGA. Markdown. It's on sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They let God in everywhere nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Supermarkets. Ladies' bathroom. Everybody's.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.01,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Parking garage. Sidewalk cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.91,0:10:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If God's going to have his way with us, I guess he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:11:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,God is both manifest and unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,God is infinite beyond time or depiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Or space or locality and has no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That which is divinity has no beginning and no end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.73,0:11:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,God is omnipresent, omnipotent, and omniscient.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.24,0:11:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to be everything, to be all that is, to know all that is knowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.24,0:11:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source and substance of consciousness, awareness, knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and sentience.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason anybody would be here today is because God is present in your consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were not for God as the presence in your consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you would not be at a lecture of this kindness.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, God, make sure that you get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The only reason you're here is because God said you should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old Doc Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a favorite of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he knows you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.94,0:12:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,He knows I'll get busy with what I'm supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.77,0:12:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Get busy with what you're supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.58,0:12:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Write another book, give another lecture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.15,0:12:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, I'm getting pooped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said about the last book.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.60,0:12:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, God, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting pooped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And a voice said, boomed,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.15,0:12:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No excuses from you, young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It boomed out of the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source and substance of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness, awareness, knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and sentience.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.84,0:13:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the sole source of the energy of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean a turtle has God's consciousness in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.05,0:13:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,A turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,A turtle has God's consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.40,0:13:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a turtle is an expression of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.85,0:13:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.26,0:13:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be kinder to the next turtle I meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,God is in the salamander.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,God is in the cougar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.78,0:13:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw a cougar in our backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.95,0:13:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.78,0:13:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a cougar, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.82,0:13:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And God was in that cougar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.54,0:14:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,God's cougar visited us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We must be somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Not everybody gets a cougar or a mountain lion in their backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.86,0:14:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, God is the source of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source of all peace, love, stillness, and beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The infinite stillness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.82,0:14:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you're walking through the woods, you're not thinking about God or divinity or anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.58,0:14:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of a sudden, the sudden stillness of the woods is like overwhelming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.14,0:14:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And when it's suddenly in the presence of divinity, without being aware that it's divinity,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.36,0:14:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the stillness and beauty of the woods is the expression of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But God is beyond all universes or materiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.05,0:14:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's the source of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond all materiality, yet the source of that very materiality.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.52,0:15:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Without God, nothing would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, that's scary, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.45,0:15:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If it wasn't for God, nothing would exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, therefore, God is the source of all existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.16,0:15:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source of all existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.01,0:15:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source of all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.36,0:15:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see if that's so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.65,0:15:34.67,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source of all that is, without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Even you and me, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that sweet?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You look at your spouse, you look at your mother, you look at your father,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.16,0:15:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,your sister and your brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you remind yourself that they are created by God
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.52,0:16:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and that changes the way you see them and behave towards them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.49,0:16:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the toad takes on a different significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.30,0:16:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Significance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.30,0:16:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When you realize that even the toad is a creation of God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.32,0:16:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So, all that is, is nothing exists except that which has been created by God.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.46,0:16:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the sole source of existence and the potentiality of beingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the ultimate context of which the universe and all the existence is the content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.04,0:16:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the a-priority, formless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.35,0:16:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the a-priority, formless.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.87,0:16:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Source of existence within all form.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So, within this cane, then, it comes forth as a cane,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,feeding away children and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.91,0:16:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of the way, children and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So, divinity is the source of everything that exists, without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.50,0:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And meditating on that can have a quite profound effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It can have quite a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.49,0:17:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It can have quite a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.75,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It can have quite a...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To look about you and realize that all that exists is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.52,0:17:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,God is not within the universe of the provable or the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.79,0:17:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's where I ran into trouble, when I was an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.77,0:17:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,As a kid, I was very profoundly religious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.46,0:17:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And one time I was walking along, walking along, not thinking about anything in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.28,0:17:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And suddenly, the totality...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.95,0:18:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The totality of the pain and suffering of mankind, I became aware of the suffering
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.25,0:18:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of all of mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.43,0:18:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And although I had been a devout believer as a child and as I grew up, when I saw the
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,complete suffering, the totality of the suffering of mankind, I became an atheist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.78,0:18:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And I became just as devout an atheist as I had been a theist.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.67,0:18:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And it took me some decades to transcend that transition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.29,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,God is not within the province of the provable or the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore atheism and theism are both foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Play with the intellect.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.38,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You can either prove God or disprove God.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source and essence of the subjective state of I-ness called enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the source and essence of the subjective state of I-ness called enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The sense of I-ness is autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no entity or person that experiences one's existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.34,0:19:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,One's existence is all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no duality between a me or an I and consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.63,0:19:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is called the state of enlightenment, the realization that that which you are is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.82,0:19:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.78,0:19:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That you are it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.46,0:19:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever there is is what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.18,0:19:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,God is the radical subjectivity of, and that's called self-realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization of the divinity, of the essence of your own existence, that nothing exists
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.47,0:19:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,other than God.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.47,0:20:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing that exists outside of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.11,0:20:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All that exists is divinity in its various forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.24,0:20:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing that exists outside of divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,God exists in its various forms, including atheism.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything that is capable of atheism is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,To be an atheist you have to have consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,To have consciousness, you have to have the presence of divinity.
