Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.30,0:25:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,was the stunning beauty the incredible beauty everything was 3d everything was
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.80,0:25:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,3d everything was three-dimensional Wow mm-hmm
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.76,0:25:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.64,0:25:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,how many people have had transformative experiences like that yes a number of
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.24,0:25:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,people thank God we thank God for that for that gift that's how we call
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.40,0:25:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment a gift it's not something that you've earned and acquired or paid
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.57,0:25:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,for etc it's like a gift from divinity suddenly you're walking along the street
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.22,0:26:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and the street lights up and you see the miraculous you see the miraculous the
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.30,0:26:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,essence of God's
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.21,0:26:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,God's gift to you as a spiritual figure in your life and I think that that is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.06,0:26:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,very important because it's the real gifts of the spiritual that God given to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.95,0:26:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you and would love to give you
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.71,0:26:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to quote a quote from a famous poet named Brendan
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.90,0:26:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,says that rather than believe the supernatural I believe in a real being
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.75,0:26:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but I believe in a real human being that is an individual that is so important to
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.39,0:26:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,me and I think that's very important to me as I'm a Christian woman I'm not just a
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.08,0:26:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Christian I'm just a Christian woman and I believe in God and I believe that that is
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.75,0:26:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,retaliation. It is beyond locality. So consciousness becomes what you become. You become aware
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.75,0:27:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that what you are is consciousness itself. Not the content of consciousness, but consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.77,0:27:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,itself. It isn't this body, it's the capacity to comprehend the existence of this body.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.90,0:27:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm. So you can exist in different realms without a body. That is true. You can exist
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.60,0:27:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,without a body. Huh. The older you get, the less you need a body, right? What good is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.50,0:27:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,it? Well, you know, I'd love to eat dinner. Loves ice cream. So we hang around for a few
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.82,0:27:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,reasons. What's the favorite ice cream right currently?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.59,0:28:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Coffee ice cream is our favorite. Okay. Anyway, as you see, that's impersonal. It just has
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.38,0:28:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to do with realizing the value of all that exists and allowing yourself the enjoyment
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.46,0:28:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and recognition of it. And so I thank God for ice cream. I thank God for ice cream.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.11,0:28:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I say, dear God, thank you for this wonderful ice cream. And the voice says, good deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.50,0:28:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then tomorrow you shall have some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.70,0:28:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the variations in the understanding, comprehension, and description of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.74,0:29:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,are widespread, widespread, depending on culture, time, age. But every culture has its own Holy
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.44,0:29:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirit, sometimes considered to be nature spirits, but still of a spiritual nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.25,0:29:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,When it's, when we need rain, I always remind the nature spirits that it hasn't rained for a month
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.56,0:29:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,now. Just in case God and the nature spirits hadn't noticed. I always remind the nature spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.16,0:29:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,when you get home, it hasn't rained for a month around here. You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.90,0:29:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. So the nature spirits sort of nudge God. And sure enough, within two weeks, it all,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.75,0:29:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,it all rains, you know. Thank you, nature spirits. All right. The variations of the depictions
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.18,0:29:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,of divinity reflect the availability of human perception and the rejections of the impediments
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.64,0:30:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego as positionalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.72,0:30:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. So we transcend all these limitations. All right. The purity of the presence of God is traditionally the essence,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.73,0:30:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ineffable quality called holiness, and is the basis for the depiction of the sacred,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.66,0:30:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that which is sacred. That which is devoid of content is the equivalent of innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.50,0:30:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in a elevated state of consciousness, you see the beauty and worth and
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.66,0:30:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.79,0:30:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,an inspiration of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always give the example,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.51,0:30:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,as you're walking down the sidewalk,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.05,0:30:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,there's this little bug walking along.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.02,0:31:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That little bug is now famous, famous little bug.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.44,0:31:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, the enlightened person carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.34,0:31:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,steps over the little bug
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.49,0:31:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,and blesses it by your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.89,0:31:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We bless the little bug because we realize
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.38,0:31:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that it represents the evolution of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.88,0:31:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,as life itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.90,0:31:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So we value life in all of its expressions.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.22,0:31:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We appreciate all of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.57,0:31:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To be appreciative of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.79,0:31:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,and the existence of all that is,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.76,0:31:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,is in itself a short course on enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.80,0:31:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I am grateful to thee, O Lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.34,0:31:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for this stage, for this audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.31,0:31:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,for this wonderful king.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.70,0:31:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thankful for the beautiful flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.51,0:31:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am thankful for a box of Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.75,0:32:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Just think, primitive man didn't have Kleenex.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.00,0:32:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He just sort of blew his nose on his sleeve,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.89,0:32:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.81,0:32:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You know where buttons come from in the military?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.75,0:32:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Military uniforms, you see, there's always buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.85,0:32:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because in cold weather,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.46,0:32:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the soldiers would all be going,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.79,0:32:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and the commander couldn't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.06,0:32:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They had buttons put on the sleeves of everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.30,0:32:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can't rub your nose,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.84,0:32:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,on your sleeve,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.79,0:32:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because of all the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.55,0:32:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So now you know what those buttons are for, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.75,0:32:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a couple of them right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.50,0:32:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God for buttons on our sleeves,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.85,0:32:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'd all be a mess to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.02,0:33:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The self is God imminent,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.41,0:33:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,shines forth of its own cord,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.50,0:33:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,just as the sun shines forth
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.27,0:33:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when the clouds are removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.93,0:33:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, you see,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.34,0:33:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,enlightenment is a totally different thing
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.56,0:33:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,than what you thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.67,0:33:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Enlightenment is a goal that I will pursue.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.67,0:33:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, you see that it is what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.67,0:33:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when you remove its barriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.81,0:33:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything to become enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.81,0:33:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,except stop being unenlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.81,0:33:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How dat?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.01,0:33:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,How dat, baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.01,0:33:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You is what is already.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.18,0:33:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I is?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.65,0:34:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, you is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.59,0:34:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.88,0:34:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.80,0:34:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,If you didn't is, you wouldn't be saying what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.34,0:34:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.59,0:34:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.59,0:34:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.19,0:34:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You're what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.73,0:34:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Something has to be there to question,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.73,0:34:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.73,0:34:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,How did I get to be where I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.73,0:34:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.38,0:34:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop being unenlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.78,0:34:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.78,0:34:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You all agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.96,0:34:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody promises they will stop being unenlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.01,0:34:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick by your agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.03,0:34:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.30,0:34:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all that there can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.17,0:34:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all that there ever was.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.17,0:34:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.13,0:34:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.71,0:34:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.71,0:34:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.71,0:35:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.71,0:35:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to read anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.26,0:35:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.26,0:35:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to sit in yoga postures and go weirdy breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.38,0:35:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.65,0:35:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.78,0:35:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how long it took.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.86,0:35:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Before it snapped, I was unenlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.86,0:35:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I snapped my finger, I've become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.28,0:35:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you notice anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.19,0:35:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.21,0:35:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just making it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.76,0:35:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you think it will make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.50,0:35:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.48,0:35:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't make me happy if you become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.96,0:35:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't care less.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.26,0:35:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to be unenlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.69,0:36:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.34,0:36:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very enlightened to let it be all right that you're not enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.63,0:36:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's okay with you that you're not enlightened, you already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.63,0:36:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit worrying about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.53,0:36:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Why seek what is?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.34,0:36:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.55,0:36:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in chasing your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.44,0:36:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No point in chasing your tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.98,0:36:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I want everybody to relax
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.98,0:36:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and to be totally complete, satisfied, and happy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.98,0:36:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,with just what you are this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.94,0:36:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.05,0:36:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody not satisfied with who or what they are this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.05,0:37:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wishes to be thrashed, trashed, and thrown overboard?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.21,0:37:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Self-awareness shines forth of its own accord
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.78,0:37:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,when the obstacles have been removed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.67,0:37:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't have to seek enlightenment at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.67,0:37:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop seeking enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.86,0:37:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.38,0:37:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.26,0:37:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.57,0:37:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody disagree?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.88,0:37:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Any stupid idiot out there that wants to disagree with the great doctor here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.88,0:38:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows everything that was ever known?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.09,0:38:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Anywhere and everywhere in the whole universe?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.09,0:38:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where I started for starters.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.44,0:38:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just stars, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.44,0:38:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,To know all that's knowable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.61,0:38:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All that's ever been known.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.61,0:38:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All that could be known.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.65,0:38:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough to do before lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.09,0:38:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.13,0:38:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,In between a peanut butter sandwich and a root beer
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.57,0:38:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,is the whole universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.92,0:38:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When you eat that peanut butter sandwich
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.92,0:38:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and you wash it down with root beer,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.92,0:38:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you've just experienced all that can be experienced
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.53,0:39:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the wondrousness and goodness of enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.53,0:39:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes it pretty easy, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.84,0:39:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, I want you to realize something.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.42,0:39:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting tired out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.17,0:39:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That what you want to happen has already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.13,0:39:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And your only problem is that you haven't recognized that it already is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.13,0:39:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.03,0:39:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible to exist and be conscious without being enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.67,0:39:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,To see that you are all that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.13,0:39:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing can exist other than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.76,0:39:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You are all there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.30,0:39:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing else.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.05,0:39:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're just a little piece of it
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.07,0:39:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,may bother what remains of your ego.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.46,0:39:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But you can't be the entire Empire State Building at one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.46,0:39:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.46,0:40:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can only be one floor at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.67,0:40:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guy was gonna jump off the Empire State Building
Dialogue: 0,0:40:06.67,0:40:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and they buckled him to the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.73,0:40:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.09,0:40:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, he was gonna jump off the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.82,0:40:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, he didn't do it, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.73,0:40:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you can say for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.76,0:40:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.76,0:40:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The wonderment of your own awareness,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.71,0:40:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own presence,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.71,0:40:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,of your own existence
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.71,0:40:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is your Empire State Building.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.98,0:40:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so used to looking at the Empire State Building,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.65,0:40:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't realize that it's one of the great wonders of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.11,0:40:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence is one of the great wonders of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.11,0:41:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That you exist
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.23,0:41:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is the ultimate miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.34,0:41:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you can see
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.86,0:41:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,the opposite would be non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.86,0:41:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got your choice between existence and non-existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.88,0:41:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only the presence of divinity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.11,0:41:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,that accords you the capacity
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.65,0:41:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to realize that you exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.65,0:41:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Other entities are,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.34,0:41:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but do not know that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.34,0:41:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They do not know that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.92,0:41:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's taking multitudes
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.50,0:41:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,of millions of years
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.30,0:41:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to move from being
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.42,0:41:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.09,0:41:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To be is one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.09,0:41:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To know that you are
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.53,0:41:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,takes millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.78,0:41:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Millennia.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.88,0:41:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.88,0:41:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeepers, creepers.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.78,0:42:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Takes millennia to exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.78,0:42:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.67,0:42:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We're the product of eons,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.67,0:42:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.61,0:42:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to move from that which is
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.61,0:42:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,to that which knows
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.69,0:42:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,that it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.69,0:42:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.03,0:42:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Billions of years
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.03,0:42:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to move from being
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.03,0:42:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.84,0:42:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.21,0:42:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a good deal or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.21,0:42:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mostly that which exists
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.21,0:42:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,does so and does not realize
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.38,0:42:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that it exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.13,0:42:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To exist and know that you exist
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.21,0:42:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,makes you enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.88,0:42:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.88,0:42:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in seeking enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.88,0:42:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone here already is enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.88,0:43:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone here knows that they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.65,0:43:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here that doesn't know that they are,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.61,0:43:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,get my gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.61,0:43:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.09,0:43:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not possible to be here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.09,0:43:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,and not know that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.09,0:43:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're here
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.44,0:43:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,means you know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.44,0:43:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.03,0:43:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.03,0:43:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no point in seeking enlightenment
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.67,0:43:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,because you already are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.69,0:43:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So the trick between the unenlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.69,0:43:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and the enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.69,0:43:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,is merely knowing the difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.88,0:43:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The unenlightened doesn't know
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.90,0:43:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're enlightened already
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.90,0:43:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore they're unenlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.86,0:43:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The enlightened knows
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.86,0:43:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that they're enlightened already
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.86,0:43:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore is enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.86,0:43:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.86,0:43:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Good deal, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.07,0:43:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody complain?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.69,0:44:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here who's not enlightened?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.94,0:44:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.40,0:44:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There are no idiots here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.48,0:44:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an audience
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.48,0:44:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,with no idiots in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.48,0:44:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How can that be?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.15,0:44:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.46,0:44:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our karma for being
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.46,0:44:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,the world's greatest teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.26,0:44:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How many teachers have you heard
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.15,0:44:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,tell me what I've told you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.96,0:44:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody know of any?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.61,0:44:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.09,0:44:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.09,0:44:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.09,0:44:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,For God's sake,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.09,0:44:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be .
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.57,0:44:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so niggardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.57,0:44:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.57,0:44:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.11,0:44:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't there any idiots out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.26,0:44:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no idiots in this audience.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.26,0:44:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What can you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.26,0:45:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.69,0:45:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.69,0:45:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that we're enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.86,0:45:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,even if we don't recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.42,0:45:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What we call enlightened
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.42,0:45:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is a person who has recognized it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.42,0:45:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,People are enlightened,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.61,0:45:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,but they are not called enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.61,0:45:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like if you're homely
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.57,0:45:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't know you're homely.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.55,0:45:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One day you look in the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.73,0:45:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.73,0:45:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,God, you are one ugly son of a gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.80,0:45:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And now you're enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.34,0:45:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what if you were a guy
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.34,0:45:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and didn't even know you were a guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.34,0:45:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.40,0:45:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday somebody says to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.40,0:45:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you're a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.40,0:45:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.40,0:45:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't even know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.40,0:45:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Or you say it to a lady,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.23,0:45:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, you're a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.23,0:45:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.23,0:46:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What if she never heard of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.36,0:46:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,She just thought everybody's like she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.36,0:46:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So consciousness then
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.96,0:46:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,is the capacity to recognize
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.96,0:46:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence of the reality
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.96,0:46:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of one's own existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.96,0:46:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The capacity to stand apart
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.11,0:46:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,and yet be that which is perceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.11,0:46:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you are both what is
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.75,0:46:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and that which realizes what is.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.82,0:46:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The unenlightened person
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.05,0:46:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,does not have that recognition.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.76,0:46:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,To be enlightened is to know that you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.76,0:46:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to know that you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.67,0:46:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and to know that you are all that can be.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.67,0:46:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than being the totality of knowingness,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.94,0:46:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,nothing else is possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.44,0:46:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That has to suffice for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.46,0:47:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.53,0:47:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.53,0:47:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.26,0:47:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.26,0:47:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.73,0:47:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.73,0:47:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.73,0:47:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,She uses threats.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.67,0:47:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You got to have lunch now.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.67,0:47:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This gentleman came,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.05,0:47:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,he's 92,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.28,0:47:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.28,0:47:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.28,0:47:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.28,0:47:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.28,0:47:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.28,0:47:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He is 92 years old
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.11,0:47:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and he said he wanted to see you
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.30,0:47:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,before he left the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.30,0:47:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.30,0:47:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.30,0:47:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He said good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.30,0:47:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.30,0:47:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.30,0:47:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.30,0:47:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.30,0:47:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.30,0:47:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.34,0:47:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.90,0:48:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That you wanted to see him
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.90,0:48:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,before you left the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.90,0:48:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so he said good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.90,0:48:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's a race
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.90,0:48:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to leave the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.90,0:48:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ahead of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.90,0:48:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I expect everything
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.11,0:48:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,to be set up when I get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.90,0:48:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I like iced tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.90,0:48:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.90,0:48:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.90,0:48:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, sit down
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.90,0:48:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and they'll be able to...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.90,0:48:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And that way they can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.69,0:48:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.69,0:48:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,my question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.69,0:48:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Eckhart Tolle says in his book
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.21,0:48:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.21,0:48:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,He says what?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.65,0:48:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,is what? That's not the new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.76,0:48:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's his latest
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.86,0:48:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,book. That
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.84,0:48:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,we will
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.86,0:48:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,stop destroying the planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.07,0:48:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,live sustainably,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.17,0:48:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,be
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.53,0:49:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,rid of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.17,0:49:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,violence, and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.32,0:49:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,kind of feel
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.92,0:49:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,along with the space brothers
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.88,0:49:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,from the different
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.42,0:49:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,planets of the Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.78,0:49:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I don't know if that's
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.84,0:49:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,in your field of
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.09,0:49:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,guessing. Eckhart Tolle said that
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.80,0:49:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be a planet
Dialogue: 0,0:49:21.96,0:49:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,with
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.65,0:49:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,little violence, and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.30,0:49:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that they would
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.07,0:49:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's hard for you to hear
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.63,0:49:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,me. It's a
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.23,0:49:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,there would be a planet with very little
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.65,0:49:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,violence, and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.92,0:49:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and they
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.50,0:49:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,would live sustainably, stop destroying
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.57,0:49:44.09,Default,,0,0,0,,the Earth, and start sharing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.38,0:49:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And that people will
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.40,0:49:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,stop destroying
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.53,0:49:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the Earth, and he wants to know if you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.50,0:49:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,see that in the future, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.86,0:49:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,People will stop destroying the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.13,0:49:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Eckhart
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.46,0:49:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tolle. I don't know who that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.78,0:50:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.23,0:50:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He wrote a book. Yes.
